<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7026134>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12–17. 12. Holaspulus tenuipes Berlese, 1904, female, venter. 13. Neparhoaspis arcuatus Petrova, 1977 female, venter. 14. Gamasholaspis gamasoides Berlese, 1904, female, venter. 15. Gamasholaspis akimotoi (Ishikawa, 1966), female, venter. 16. Krantzolaspina angustatus (Ishikawa, 1987), female, venter. 17. Parholaspulus alstoni Evans, 1956, female, venter. Scale bar: 140 μm for 12; 130 µm for 13; 107 μm for 14; 120 μm for 15; 130 μm for 16; 115 μm for 17." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7026134/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

